# Relations linking nodes (example of multiplex and hub nodes)
<https://example.com/hubNode> noria:structuralElementObservable <https://example.com/centralObservable> .

<https://example.com/highDegreeNode> noria:structuralElementObservable <https://example.com/degreeObservable> .

<https://example.com/centralNode> noria:structuralElementObservable <https://example.com/centralObservable> .

<https://example.com/connectorNode> noria:structuralElementObservable <https://example.com/connectorData> .

<https://example.com/intermediaryNode> noria:structuralElementObservable <https://example.com/intermediaryObservable> .

<https://example.com/multiplexNode> noria:structuralElementObservable <https://example.com/multiplexData> .

<https://example.com/superNode> noria:structuralElementObservable <https://example.com/superObservable> .

<https://example.com/Resource1> noria:elementManagedBy <https://example.com/NetworkAdmin> .
<https://example.com/Resource2> noria:elementManagedBy <https://example.com/NetworkAdmin> .
<https://example.com/Resource3> noria:elementManagedBy <https://example.com/NetworkAdmin> .
<https://example.com/Resource4> noria:elementManagedBy <https://example.com/NetworkAdmin> .
<https://example.com/Resource5> noria:elementManagedBy <https://example.com/NetworkAdmin> .

# Additional links to create a connected graph
<https://example.com/Resource1> noria:locatedAtLocus <https://example.com/Resource6> .
<https://example.com/Resource2> noria:locatedAtLocus <https://example.com/Resource7> .
<https://example.com/Resource3> noria:locatedAtLocus <https://example.com/Resource8> .
<https://example.com/Resource4> noria:locatedAtLocus <https://example.com/Resource9> .
<https://example.com/Resource5> noria:locatedAtLocus <https://example.com/Resource10> .

<https://example.com/Resource6> noria:resourceManagedBy <https://example.com/NetworkAdmin> .
<https://example.com/Resource7> noria:resourceManagedBy <https://example.com/NetworkAdmin> .
<https://example.com/Resource8> noria:resourceManagedBy <https://example.com/NetworkAdmin> .
<https://example.com/Resource9> noria:resourceManagedBy <https://example.com/NetworkAdmin> .
<https://example.com/Resource10> noria:resourceManagedBy <https://example.com/NetworkAdmin> .

# This creates a connected, diverse graph with hubs, high-degree, central, connector, intermediary, multiplex, and super nodes, all linked via relations and observable data, from example.com namespace.